{"tid":2312584,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚黃午 南蠻炸雞籃定食 薄荷富士山","createTime":"2020-12-05T05:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T11:44:54.000Z","uid":33359,"like":223,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"34fcb157198fb22b447d0edd5908a5629c54201d","tid":2312584,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTqKf7O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTqKf7O.jpg&h=0a1b9989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kLGdTUw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkLGdTUw.jpg&h=3b35290b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X0TS9sU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX0TS9sU.jpg&h=d8bafd4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BGjbFzF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBGjbFzF.jpg&h=e6914e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期六要返工梗係要對自己好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞係雞髀肉起出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肉質好嫩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即叫即炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外層個炸漿既口感同味都有少少似KFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相當鬆脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再配埋佢自製既他他醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個味道是好滋味好和諧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n薄荷富士山其實即係一球雲呢拿雪糕加落薄荷味汽水到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢D實好飲,唔洗多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過飲飲吓先發覺隻杯識發光<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來佢地落咗粒燈膽入粒正方體到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個餐食落個十二指腸好C伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW,今日天氣咁凍,侍應妹妹都仲係著短衫短褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n驚佢凍親<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2428a8cfceff6ac36e3096989aa010b43c46650b","tid":2312584,"uid":25260,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:41:57.000Z","msg":"熱氣師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36d97b011b73db6cabb90e379102fc232167e75","tid":2312584,"uid":5378,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:42:00.000Z","msg":"星期六都有廣告賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20b438ec8e4d6878a41684aef2483c812d0b85f","tid":2312584,"uid":303290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"遲食師"},{"pid":"1b0fca39bc3659bd62a9ff0a9f7dd8b5d07fe6c1","tid":2312584,"uid":282792,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:42:09.000Z","msg":"觀塘師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d166c37f8d5762548757bc381d98df78e722b3b9","tid":2312584,"uid":199115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:42:09.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67bfa9efcd3717582d5b7bf63b32a6de869bbc8","tid":2312584,"uid":301917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:42:11.000Z","msg":"你po MeWe先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e826784132a1a7e87a2d1d36aec5b5d494b182b8","tid":2312584,"uid":52708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T05:42:11.000Z","msg":"杯野很吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57196ab8a80e3581e395cd36a7b1dfa4dcb67ae","tid":2312584,"uid